{"tid":265031,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"[僱傭條例] 劈炮賠錢一問","createTime":"2017-05-31T10:22:10.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-31T13:46:48.000Z","uid":4880,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"aa96499be3e557bf12499147efe2a97d5732966a","tid":265031,"uid":4880,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-31T10:22:10.000Z","msg":"話說返新工時簽左份濕鳩agreement，同意左過試用期後某period內辭職就會賠一舊錢（佢炒我佢唔使賠<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ）<br />\n<br />\n咁依家公司入面啲八婆同撚樣就日鳩日西面同俾說話我聽，搞到我日撚日起身都好驚要返去同精神受到極大困擾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 但劈炮嘅話就要一個月通知同賠果舊錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n問：除左搏炒外有冇方法可以唔賠舊錢而離職？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 有勞各方巴絲賜教，帶我脫離苦海<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"408358b5a7f777187cf444e792bf25ebace9a249","tid":265031,"uid":4880,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-31T10:39:31.000Z","msg":"Push <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3e4e1f59f42fc92cced31b4ce9100397bbaacf78","tid":265031,"uid":33483,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-31T10:43:00.000Z","msg":"點解佢炒你唔洗賠 有冇條款睇下"},{"pid":"12f396cff98169b9d50542b19623d241343298a8","tid":265031,"uid":8000,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-31T10:43:05.000Z","msg":"岸鳩仔<br />\n坐係度乜都唔撚做<br />\n屌撚佢地老母<br />\n佢冇得唔炒你"},{"pid":"b129a21f550b4f36e8171c9d1a702e8fe5600512","tid":265031,"uid":8000,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-31T10:43:29.000Z","msg":"岸鳩<br />\n邊度炒人都要賠"},{"pid":"a48ba37abf58de08e1f8bd2a285297ccea21c1ca","tid":265031,"uid":1166,"